<title>为什么农民不愿缴医疗保险了？</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%84%BF%E7%BC%B4%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9F</link>
